OL,3,CTeenager charged after boiling water
OL,4,Callegedly thrown on prison guard
OL,6,FA teenager has been charged after a
OL,7,Fprison guard at Wetherby Young
OL,8,FOffender Institution allegedly had
OL,9,Fboiling water thrown over him.
OL,11,FThe 17-year-old boy was charged with
OL,12,Fcausing actual bodily harm after an
OL,13,Fincident in June 2025 in which a
OL,14,Fprison officer was injured.
OL,16,FCounter Terrorism Policing North East
OL,17,Fsaid the teenage British inmate
OL,18,Fremains in custody.
OL,20,FThe boy is set to appear at Leeds
OL,21,FMagistrates Court on 12 May.
